snippet.title: Crossy Road Castle Console - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Climb castles with the Crossy Road crew in this cross platform online multiplayer arcade platformer. Shoot out of cannons, ride rainbows, and make your way through a maze of never-ending levels. The award winning Apple Arcade hit is coming soon to Nintendo Switch™, PlayStation®5, Xbox X|S, Xbox One!

🐔 Join the community & follow Crossy Road on social media! 
⭑  Discord: https://discord.gg/crossyroadcentral
